aycottages.co.uk|website=Bridport Holiday Cottages|accessdate=28 January 2018}}</ref> Askerswell, [[Bridport]]\n*Maiden Newton Mill, [[Maiden Newton]]\n*Mangerton Mill, [[Bridport]]\n*Pegg's Farm Mill, [[Iwerne Minster]]\n*Place Mill, [[Christchurch, Dorset|Christchurch]]\n*Sturminster Newton Mill, [[Sturminster Newton]]\n*Town Mill, [[Lyme Regis]]\n*White Mill, [[Sturminster Marshall]]\n*Upwey Mill, [[Weymouth, Dorset|Weymouth]]\n\n===Durham===\n*[[Brignall Mill]], [[River Greta, Durham|River Greta]]\n*[[Killhope Wheel]], [[Weardale]]\n*[[Path Head Mill]], [[Blaydon]]\n\n===Essex===\n[[File:Bourne Mill.jpg|thumb|Bourne Mill, Essex]]\n*Bourne Mill, [[Colchester]]\n*[[Thorrington Tide Mill]], [[Thorrington]]\n*[[Alderford Mill]], [[Sible Hedingham]]\n*Beeleigh Mill, [Maldon, Essex]\n\n===Gloucestershire===\n*[[Dean Heritage Centre]], [[Cinderford]]\n*[[Owlpen Manor]], [[Gloucestershire]], with bolting, cleaning and winnowing machinery, dated 1728\n*[[Stanway Watermill]], Stanway, [[Cheltenham]]\n\n===Hampshire===\n[[File:Sadler's Mill 2005.jpg|thumb|Sadler's Mill, Hampshire]]\n*[[Alderholt Mill]], [[Fordingbridge]]\n*[[Chesapeake Mill]], [[Wickham, Hampshire]]\n*[[Eling Tide Mill]], [[Totton and Eling|Eling]]\n*[[Headley Water Mill]], [[Headley, East Hampshire|Headley]]\n*[[Longbridge Mill]], [[Sherfield on Loddon]]\n*[[Quay Mill, Emsworth]]\n*[[Rooksbury Mill]], [[Andover, Hampshire|Andover]]\n*[[Sadler's Mill]], [[Romsey]]\n*[[Whitchurch Silk Mill]], [[Whitchurch, Hampshire|Whitchurch]]\n*[[Winchester City Mill]], [[Winchester]]\n*[[Woodmill Southampton|Woodmill]], [[Southampton]]\n\n===Hertfordshire===\n[[File:Redbournbury Watermill.jpg|thumb|Redbournbury Mill, Hertfordshire]]\n*[[Kingsbury Watermill]], St Albans\n*[[Mill Green Watermill]], Hatfield\n*[[Redbournbury Mill]], Redbourn\n\n===Isle of Wight===\n*[[Calbourne Mill]], Calbourne]\n\n===Kent===\n[[File:Bradley's Mill, Speldhurst.jpg|thumb|Bradley's Mill, Speldhurst, Kent]]\n*Wandle Mill, [[Benenden]]\n*[[Crabble Corn Mill]], [[Dover]]\n*[[Haxted Watermill]], near [[Edenbridge, Kent|Edenbridge]] - now a Surrey mill. (Medway)\n*Chart Gunpowder Mills, [[Faversham]]\n*Hever Watermill, [[Hever, Kent|Hever]] (Medway)\n*Hythe Watermill, [[Hythe, Kent|Hythe]]\n*Swanton Mill, [[Mersham]] (Stour)\n*Periwinkle Mill, [[Milton Regis]]\n*Ryarsh Mill, [[Ryarsh]] (Medway)\n*Ashbourne Mill, [[Tenterden]]\n*See also:-\n**[[Medway watermills]]\n***[[Medway watermills (lower tributaries)]]\n***[[Medway watermills (middle tributaries)]]\n***[[Medway watermills (upper tributaries)]]\n**[[Stour watermills]]\n\n===Lancashire===\n*[[Helmshore Mills Textile Museum|Higher Mill]], [[Helmshore]], [[Borough of Rossendale|Rossendale]]\n*[[Thurnham Mill]], [[River Conder|Conder Green]]\n*[[Halton-on-Lune|Forge Bank Mill, Halton]]\n\n===Leicestershire===\n*[[Claybrooke]] Mill\n*[[Mill On The Soar]], [[Broughton Astley]]\n*[[Shepshed]] Watermill\n\n===Lincolnshire===\n*[[Alvingham Mill]], [[Alvingham]]\n*[[Cogglesford Mill]], [[Sleaford]]\n*[[Claythorpe Mill]], [[Aby]]\n*[[Tealby Mill]], [[Tealby]]\n\n===London===\n*[[Grove Park, Carshalton#Upper Mill|Upper Mill]], [[Carshalton]]\n*[[Three Mills]] tide mill, [[Bromley-by-Bow]]\n\n===Norfolk===\n[[File:Caley Mill - home of Norfolk Lavender, Heacham, Norfolk - geograph.org.uk - 1731715.jpg|thumb|Caley Mill aka Heacham Mill, Norfolk]]\n*[[Scarrow Beck#Aldborough Watermill|Aldborough Watermill]] on [[Scarrow Beck]]\n*[[Bolwick Hall|Bolwick Hall Watermill]] on the Mermaid\n*[[River Cong (Norfolk)#Congham Oil Mill|Congham Oil Mill]] near [[Congham]]\n*[[River Ainse (or Eyn)#Eade's watermill|Eade\u2019s Watermill]] at [[Great Witchingham]]\n*[[River Mun#Gimingham watermill|Gimingham Watermill]] on the [[River Mun]]\n*[[Gur Beck#Gresham Watermill|Gresham Watermill]], Gresham,\n*[[Hagon Beck#Gunton Park Sawmill|Gunton Park Sawmill]], [[Gunton Hall|Gunton Park]], North Norfolk\n*[[River Heacham#Heacham Watermill|Heacham Watermill]]\n*[[Hempstead Watermill]]\n*[