ford]]\n*[[Stoke Mill, Guildford]]\n\n===East Sussex===\n*[[Bateman's#Mill|Bateman's Park MIll]], [[Burwash]]\n*[[Michelham Priory Mill]], [[Hailsham]]\n*[[Park Mill]], [[Etchingham]]\n*[[Tide Mills, East Sussex|Tide Mills]], [[Newhaven, East Sussex|Newhaven]]\n*See also:-\n**[[Medway watermills]]\n\n===West Sussex===\n[[File:Westhampnett Mill, Sussex - geograph.org.uk - 1759735.jpg|thumb|Westhampnett Mill, West Sussex]]\n*[[Coultershaw Wharf and Beam Pump|Coultershaw Beam Pump]], [[Petworth]]\n*[[Ifield Water Mill]], [[Crawley]]\n*[[Weald and Downland Open Air Museum#Watermill|Lurgashall Watermill]], [[Singleton, West Sussex|Singleton]]\n*[[Westhampnett|Westhampnett Mill]]\n\n===Tyne and Wear===\n*[[Path Head Watermill]], [[Blaydon]]\n\n===Warwickshire===\n[[File:Wellesbourne Water Mill - geograph.org.uk - 89870.jpg|thumb|Wellesbourne Water Mill, Warwickshire]]\n*[[Arrow Mill]], Arrow, Alcester<ref>[http://www.arrowmill.com/ Arrow Millofficial website]</ref> Hotel with waterwheel in restaurant.\n*[[Charlecote Mill]], [[Stratford-upon-Avon]]<ref>[http://www.charlecotemill.co.uk/ Charlecote Mill official website]</ref>\n*[[Saxon Mill]], Warwick\n*[[Wellesbourne Watermill]], [[Wellesbourne]]\n\n===West Midlands===\n*[[New Hall Mill]], [[Sutton Coldfield]]<ref>[http://www.newhallmill.org.uk/ New Hall Mill official website]</ref>\n*[[Sarehole Mill]], [[Hall Green]], [[Birmingham]]<ref>[http://www.bmag.org.uk/sarehole-mill Sarehole MillOfficial Website] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100403093342/http://www.bmag.org.uk/sarehole-mill |date=2010-04-03 }}</ref>\n\n===Wiltshire===\n*[[Coleshill Mill]], [[Swindon]]\n\n===North Yorkshire===\n[[File:Gayle Mill, North Yorkshire.JPG|thumb|Gayle Mill, North Yorkshire]]\n*[[Darley, North Yorkshire|Darley Mill Centre]], [[Nidderdale]]\n*[[Fountains Abbey Mill]], [[Ripon]]\n*[[Gayle Mill, North Yorkshire|Gayle Mill]], [[Hawes]], [[Wensleydale]]<ref>[http://www.gaylemill.org.uk/ Gayle Mill official website]</ref>\n*[[Howsham Mill]], [[Malton, North Yorkshire|Malton]]\n*[[Pateley Bridge Watermill]], [[Nidderdale]]\n*[[Raindale Mill]], [[York]]\n* Tocketts Mill, [[Guisborough]]\n* Low Mill, [[Bainbridge, North Yorkshire|Bainbridge]], Wensleydale\n\n===South Yorkshire===\n[[File:Worsbrough Mill 2005.jpg|thumb|Worsbrough Mill, South Yorkshire]]\n*[[Abbeydale Industrial Hamlet]], [[Sheffield]]\n*[[Shepherd Wheel]], [[Sheffield]]\n*[[Wilsons of Sharrow]], [[Sheffield]]\n*[[Top Forge]], [[Thurgoland]]\n*[[Worsbrough Mill]], [[Barnsley]]\n{{-}}\n\n===West Yorkshire===\n[[File:Armley Mills, Leeds - geograph.org.uk - 615329.jpg|thumb|Armley Mills, Leeds, West Yorkshire]]\n*[[Armley Mills]], [[Armley]]\n*[[Scarcroft Watermill]]\n*[[Thwaite Mills]], [[Leeds]]\n*[[Queen's Mill]], [[Castleford]]\n\n===Worcestershire===\n*[[Churchill Forge Mill]], [[Churchill, Worcestershire|Churchill]]\n*[[Fladbury Watermill]], [[Worcestershire]]\n*[[Forge Mill Needle Museum|Forge Mill]], [[Redditch]]\n\n== Scotland ==\n\n===Aberdeenshire===\n*[[Benholm Mill]], [[Benholm]] near [[Johnshaven]], [[Kincardineshire]]\n\n===Angus===\n[[File:Barry Mill2.jpg|thumb|Barry Mill, Angus]]\n*[[Barry Mill]], [[Carnoustie]]\n\n===Dumfries and Galloway===\n*[[Barburgh Mill, Closeburn]]\n*[[Enterkinfoot and the Enterkin Pass|Enterkin Mill]]\n*[[Mennock|Mennock Mill]]\n*[[New Abbey Mill]], New Abbey\n\n===East Ayrshire===\n[[File:Aiket Mill.JPG|thumb|Aiket Mill, East Ayrshire]]\n*[[Barony of Aiket|Aiket Mill]], [[Dunlop, East Ayrshire|Dunlop]]\n*[[Kirkwood Estate, East Ayrshire|Bloak Mill]], [[Dunlop, East Ayrshire|Dunlop]]\n*[[Busbie Castle|Busbie Mill]], [[Knockentiber]]\n*[[Dalmore House and Estate|Dalmore Mill]], [[Stair, East Ayrshire|Stair]]\n*[[Dalmusternock, East Ayrshire|Dalmusternock Mill]]\n*Drumastle Mill, [[Dalry, North Ayrshire|Dalry]]\n*Giffen Mill, [[Barrmill]]\n*[[Kilmaurs Place|Kilmaurs Mill]], [[Kilmaurs]]\n*[[Loch Brown|Ladeside Mill]], [[Mauchline]]\n*[[Laigh Milton Viaduct|Laigh Milton Mill]], [[Gatehead]]